{"title_page": "Shoi Sakaguchi", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Orphan|date=October 2017}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Shoi Sakaguchi\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Shoi Sakaguchi\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1999|5|7}}\n|birth_place=[[Tokyo]], [[Japan]]\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.74}}\n|position=[[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n|currentclub=[[FC Tokyo]]\n|clubnumber=49\n|youthyears1=|youthclubs1=[[FC Tokyo]]\n|years1=2016\u2013|clubs1=[[FC Tokyo]]|caps1=|goals1=\n|totalcaps=|totalgoals=\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update=\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Shoi Sakaguchi'''|\u5742\u53e3 \u7965\u5c09|Sakaguchi Sh\u014di|born May 7, 1999}} is a [[Japanese people|Japanese]] [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=19683 J.League Data Site]</ref> He plays for [[FC Tokyo]].\n\n==Career==\nShoi Sakaguchi joined [[FC Tokyo]] in 2016. On November 5, he debuted in [[J3 League]] (v [[AC Nagano Parceiro]]).<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=19683 J.League Data Site]</ref><ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFMS02/?match_card_id=18885 Match report J.League Data Site]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player|19683}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sakaguchi, Shoi}}\n[[Category:1999 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Tokyo]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:J3 League players]]\n[[Category:FC Tokyo players]]\n[[Category:FC Tokyo U-23 players]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-defender-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=October 2017}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Shoi Sakaguchi\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Shoi Sakaguchi\n|birth_date={{Birth dat